Subject: ERR_CONNECTION_RESET error while accessing websites
Description: The user could open kayak.nl but couldn't open kayak.pl. Same result both in Chrome & Edge. Restart of EPP didn't help. Once the agent service is unloaded using the Win tool, the page successfully loaded. The user started the service shortly after loading the page and it is working. Probably related, during the issue, Zoom Workspace was complaining about not being able to sync calendar. Attaching the diagnostics.
What_We_Know__c: EPP causes the following error: "ERR_CONNECTION_RESET error" when accessing websites
Next_Steps__c: A test build was provided to the customer and I'm waiting for the confirmation if the issue is addressed.
